  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list>
<item>Explain how simultaneity and length contraction are related.</item>
<item>Describe the relation between length contraction and time dilation and use it to derive the length-contraction equation.</item>
</list></md:abstract>
